version_description: I found the chords myself and they are different than the others

In the intro when he picks the low F he uses his thumb. When there's a C with an asterisk you just play the intro. You can also give some extra flavour by using C2 and Fmaj7 as quick chords where specified.
Full and detailed fingerstyle parts with RH fingering guide.
Reformatted Verses and Choruses and removed dashes between chords.
